# This directory stores SSL certificates
# 
# For development, generate self-signed certificates:
#   Linux/Mac: ./scripts/generate-ssl-cert.sh
#   Windows: .\scripts\generate-ssl-cert.ps1
#
# For production, place your certificates here:
#   - cert.pem (or path specified in SSL_CERT_PATH)
#   - key.pem (or path specified in SSL_KEY_PATH)
#   - ca.pem (optional, path specified in SSL_CA_PATH)

